BGPmon-Validate version 0.1
========================

BGPmon-Validate is a collection of Perl functions that
are useful to validate an XML message from a BGPmon instance
against the published XSD.

- Validator.pm allows one to easily validate an XML message
  against the current XSD.

This module should allow rapid validation of XML messages in clients
that make use of the BGPmon data.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Test
  XML::LibXML
  BGPmon::Fetch

